OL,5, The government is proposing to give all
OL,6, employees the right to request flexible
OL,7, working when they start new jobs, the  
OL,8, BBC understands.                       
OL,10,FA consultation is to be launched on the
OL,11,Fproposals this week.                   
OL,13,FThe plan would allow all UK employees  
OL,14,Fto request a flexible working          
OL,15,Farrangement from their first day at a  
OL,16,Fnew employer.                          
OL,18,FAt the moment, workers have to wait    
OL,19,Funtil they have been in their role for 
OL,20,Fsix months.                            
